	<string name="help_title">Help &amp; Feedback</string>
	<string name="help_intro">This sample demonstrates Markdown translation with
		ML Kit while preserving Markdown structure.</string>
	<string name="help_how_it_works_title">How translation works</string>
	<string name="help_how_it_works_body">• Parses Markdown into an AST/token stream\n•
		Translates only human-readable text\n• Preserves code blocks, links,
		URLs, and layout\n• Rebuilds Markdown in original structure\n• Falls
		back to regex protection when AST preparation fails</string>
	<string name="help_api_notes_title">API notes</string>
	<string name="help_api_notes_body">• Use one MlKitMarkdownTranslator instance per
		screen scope\n• Download language models before translation\n•
		explainMarkdown() is local diagnostics and does not call
		translation\n• close() translator when owner is destroyed</string>
